author: eTN Editor
title: New President and COO at Un-Cruise Adventures
text:
New President and COO at Un-Cruise Adventures Adv: Tim Jacox Adv: 
Small ship cruise line Un-Cruise Adventures announced today that a company longtime executive is stepping into a new role at the line as President and Chief Operations Officer. The adventure and river cruise company has a fleet of eight ships and sails in Alaska, Columbia/Snake Rivers, the Pacific Northwest, Mexico, Hawaii, and Central and South America.
